  -- We have h1 : {x | p x ‚ąß q x} ‚ąą ūĚďĚ x
  -- We have h2 : {x | p' x ‚ąß q' x} ‚ąą ūĚďĚ x
  -- The set we want is the union of the sets in h1 and h2
